function Start(listValidActors, idActorDetector)

	local bPlayersOnPlate = false
	
	for i, playerID in pairs(listValidActors) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsAlive(playerID) then
			bPlayersOnPlate = true
			break
		end
	end
	
	if bPlayersOnPlate then
		pressurePlatePressed(idActorDetector, true, false)
	else
		pressurePlatePressed(idActorDetector, false, false)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	
	for i, actorID in pairs(Hydra.ActorsInTriggerBounds(idActorDetector)) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsPlayer(actorID) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(actorID) then
			return
		end
	end

	pressurePlatePressed(idActorDetector, false, false)
end

	removeChargingEffect(idActorChargeable)
	
	Hydra.ActorDelete(Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorChargeable, "minimapGizmo")[1])
	
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idFXProxy, 8)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idFXProxy, EG_RUNE_COMPLETE)
	
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_CHARGEABLE_OBELISK, EG_SFX_RUNE_COMPLETE_ON_OBELISK)

	Hydra.BuffRemove(POWER_INCREMENTER, "ACTIVE", idActorChargeable)
	Hydra.BuffRemove(POWER_INCREMENTER, "PLATE_ACTIVE", idSwitch)
	Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(POWER_INCREMENTER, "DONE", idActorChargeable)
	Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(POWER_INCREMENTER, "PLATE_DONE", idSwitch)
	
	Hydra.ChargeableGizmoStart(ID_CHARGEABLE_BLOOD)

	if nRunesCompleted == 1 then -- turn on / trigger spawners when points are captured
	
		for i, spawnerID in pairs(Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(ID_THIS_QUEST, S_POINTCAPTURED_SPAWNER_AMBIENT)) do
--			Hydra.ActorEnable(spawnerID)
			Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(ID_THIS_QUEST, spawnerID)
		end
		
		Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(ID_THIS_QUEST, S_SPAWNER_BRUTE)
		
	elseif nRunesCompleted == 2 then
	
		Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(ID_ELITE_SPAWNER)
		
	elseif nRunesCompleted == 3 then
	
		for i, spawnerID in pairs(Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(ID_THIS_QUEST, S_POINTCAPTURED_SPAWNER_AMBIENT)) do
--			Hydra.ActorEnable(spawnerID)
			Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(ID_THIS_QUEST, spawnerID)
		end
		
		Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(ID_THIS_QUEST, S_SPAWNER_BRUTE)
		
	end
end

local function removeChargingEffect(idActor)
	if Hydra.ActorComplexEffectIsValid(idActor, tChargingFX[idActor]) then
		Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffect(idActor, tChargingFX[idActor])
		tChargingFX[idActor] = nil
	end
end

local function trySpawnChampion(idActorChargeable)
	
	if TableContains(N_CHAMP_PLATE_SPAWNS, nRunesCompleted) then
		Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(idActorChargeable, S_CP_SPAWNER_3)
	end

end


local function pressurePlatePressed(idTrigger, bPressed, bActive)
	local idSwitch = T_TRIGGER_SWITCH_PAIRS[idTrigger]
	local idActorChargeable = T_TRIGGER_CHARGEABLE_PAIRS[idTrigger]
	local bSwitchOn = Hydra.ActorGizmoSwitchIsOn(idSwitch)

	if bPressed then
		if not bSwitchOn then
			Hydra.ActorGizmoOperate(idSwitch, Hydra.ACDID_INVALID, false)
			
			if bActive and not Hydra.ChargeableGizmoIsCharging(idActorChargeable) then
				Hydra.ChargeableGizmoStart(idActorChargeable)
				tChargingFX[idActorChargeable] = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idActorChargeable, EG_SFX_BLOOD_CHARGING, true)
				tChargingFX[idSwitch] = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idSwitch, EG_RUNE_CHARGING, true)
			end
		end
	elseif bSwitchOn then
	
		Hydra.ActorGizmoOperate(idSwitch, Hydra.ACDID_INVALID, false)
		
		if bActive and Hydra.ChargeableGizmoIsCharging(idActorChargeable) then
			Hydra.ChargeableGizmoStop(idActorChargeable)
			removeChargingEffect(idSwitch)
			removeChargingEffect(idActorChargeable)
		end
	end
end

local function checkShouldStopBloodChargeable(nIndex)
	if nRunesCompleted == nIndex then
		Hydra.ChargeableGizmoStop(ID_CHARGEABLE_BLOOD)
	end
end

T_TRIGGER_SWITCH_PAIRS = {}

tChargingFX = {}
nRunesCompleted = 0

for i, idTrigger in pairs(T_TRIGGERS) do -- some table set up
	T_TRIGGER_CHARGEABLE_PAIRS[idTrigger] = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idTrigger, "chargeable")[1]

end

for i, idMob in pairs(Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(ID_THIS_QUEST, "introMob")) do -- make intro mobs taunt loop
